metadata.title: Eastern Chukchi Sea - Alaska USGS Open File Report 86-405

creators.name: Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), National Environmental Satellite, Data
Information Service (NESDIS), National Geophysical Data Center (NGDC)

metadata.description:
Approximately 2,652 km of 24-channel seismic-reflection
profiles in the Eastern Chukchi Sea are now available for
purchase from the National Geophysical Data Center (NGDC).  These
data were collected in early September 1980 by the U.S.
Geological Survey (USGS) Research Vessel S.P. LEE during Cruise
L880AR.  The USGS, Department of Interior has provided these
profiles to NGDC for public dissemination.
